{"id":172615,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/08/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011816/","date":"2011-08-17T02:00:20Z","modified":"2011-08-17T05:44:55Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/8/16","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span>@xiaomi2020</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《中国争议》博客：</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinadebate.com/2011/08/ai-weiwei-dissident-parole-violator-and-heir-to-mike-the-headless-chicken/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">艾未未出狱后比以前更有影响力</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，杀鸡儆猴未成反折了一把米，中国政府得想新招</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《曼谷邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bangkokpost.com/breakingnews/251963/china-must-free-rights-lawyer-gao\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">欧洲议会主席布泽克周一呼吁中国释放律师和人权活动家高智</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">晟</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：尽管胡锦涛誓言稳定，中国公民面临更复杂的舆论引导和控制，然而</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/16/world/asia/16dalian.html?_r=1\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大规模抗议和公众表达将成为常</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">态</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/16/world/asia/16tibet.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">一位</span>29<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">岁的僧人周一在四川省藏区道孚自焚身亡</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；继格尔登寺自焚事件以来，这是</span></span><span><span>5</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个月内第二起僧人自焚。新华社也报道了这一消息，但是没有提供细节</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>BBC </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">问答：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-pacific-14533879\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国与藏族人（已认领</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《美国之音》：中国政府称，在未来五年内，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.voanews.com/english/news/asia/Beijing-to-Subsidize-Conservation-of-Tibets-Grassland-127798608.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">每年将投资超过</span>3<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美元，以保护西藏的草原</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《洞察中国》博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinasignpost.com/2011/08/china%E2%80%99s-s-curve-trajectory-structural-factors-will-likely-slow-the-growth-of-china%E2%80%99s-economy-and-comprehensive-national-power/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">结构性因素将使得中国经济和国力增长速度放缓</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-15/china-home-sales-skirt-policies-with-fake-divorces-parking-lots.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">为了绕过房控政策，中国人选择假离婚，甚至真离婚</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。地产商花样百出，送车库、花园、阁楼；帮助贷款，延迟首付等等</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">讨论最近报道的巴基斯坦让中国工程师检查美坠毁直升机：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2011/OPINION/08/15/cronin.pakistan.china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">巴基斯坦是不是把美国给卖了</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">？</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《路透社》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/08/15/usa-china-biden-idUSN1E77E11A20110815\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">拜登访华</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：将于习近平在北京和成都共进晚餐；</span></span><span><span>4</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">天之行的主要话题是赤字和台湾；也会访问蒙古、日本</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《悉尼晨报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.smh.com.au/world/cameron-blames-moral-collapse-for-riots-20110816-1iv9g.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡梅隆周一宣布，他将重新检讨政府政策，以挽回社会</span>“<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">道德逐渐沦丧</span>”<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的局势</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；他认为这是伦敦骚乱的原因</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>CNN </span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2011/WORLD/asiapcf/08/15/japan.nuclear/index.html?eref=rss_world&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed:+rss/cnn_world+(RSS:+World)&#038;utm_content=Google+Reader\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">日本将在环境省下设置原子能安全厅，管理核能利用安全问题</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《悉尼晨报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.smh.com.au/breaking-news-world/nkorea-warns-of-war-as-usskorea-exercise-20110816-1ivhx.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">韩美举行大规模联合军演</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，北朝鲜斥之为挑衅，警告可能引发</span></span><span><span>“</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">全面战争</span></span><span><span>”</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》：旧金山联邦储备银行的一份研究发现，进口中国产品只占美国总消费</span></span><span><span>1.9%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">；即使</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://economix.blogs.nytimes.com/2011/08/15/made-in-china-but-still-profiting-americans/?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在</span>1<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美元中国进口产品中，仅有</span>45<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美分付给中国</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">旧金山联储银行的研究报告原文：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.frbsf.org/publications/economics/letter/2011/el2011-25.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“中国制造”的美国内容</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——欢迎有兴趣的译者翻译</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-16/s-p-downgraded-in-treasury-trade-after-upgrade-for-china.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">标普升级共产党中国信用评级，却降级美国国债评级。此举受到市场批</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">评</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-15/china-increased-treasury-holdings-for-third-month-in-june-as-demand-waned.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国连续第三个月增持美国国债</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，达到</span></span><span><span>1.17</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万亿美元；亚洲国家增持国债。自</span></span><span><span>2009</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年以来，由于担忧国债前景，外国投资者首次净卖出美国国债</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《路透印度版》：中国国有证券杂志在头版社论中说，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://in.reuters.com/article/2011/08/16/idINIndia-58799720110816\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">放宽人民币兑美元浮动范围的时机已经成熟</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-08-15/foreign-direct-investment-in-china-jumps-20-to-8-3-billion.html\">7<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">月，中国的国际直接投资达到</span>83<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美元</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，比去年同期增长</span></span><span><span>20%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《中国见红》博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/08/12/going-to-the-hospital-in-china-a-few-tips-for-medical-emergencies-in-the-middle-kingdom/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">老外在中国看病注意事项</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：找个同伴，带现金，准备吊盐水，不要指望舒适，相信你的医生</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《中国日报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/china/2011-08/15/content_13109329.htm\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">江西赣州龙南一位农民，因为帮助朋友安乐死，被判</span>2<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年徒刑</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">。此判决在中国引发讨</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">论</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span>McClatchy</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.mcclatchydc.com/2011/08/14/120620/womans-effort-to-have-rapist-tried.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">从一桩妇女强奸案看中国法制缺陷</span></a></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>友情提示：译者Podcast已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.c